and you fucking abandoned me!

632
00:41:58,960 --> 00:42:00,564
That's not true!

633
00:42:05,200 --> 00:42:06,660
You're not going anywhere. Stay there.

634
00:42:06,760 --> 00:42:09,060
Get off of me!

635
