(SCREAMS)

636
00:42:32,560 --> 00:42:33,800
Fucker!

637
00:42:35,440 --> 00:42:36,726
You son of a bitch!

638
00:42:37,440 --> 00:42:40,887
Roger! Get the fuck off me!

639
00:42:44,800 --> 00:42:47,700
I didn't abandon you.

640
00:42:47,800 --> 00:42:50,041
You left home, for God's sake!

641
