00:43:43,880 --> 00:43:45,340
All at once or slow?

655
00:43:45,440 --> 00:43:47,124
- Mm?
- Slow.

656
00:43:49,080 --> 00:43:51,140
(SCREAMS)

657
00:43:51,240 --> 00:43:52,900
Fuck!

