671
00:44:36,760 --> 00:44:38,740
will actually help the child,

672
00:44:38,840 --> 00:44:40,940
that it'll do the right thing,

673
00:44:41,040 --> 00:44:44,169
but it doesn't always.

674
00:44:45,680 --> 00:44:47,330
